data.description: Come see this corner block home located in Magnolia with territorial and partial view of the mountains. This cape cod home was built in 1944 and offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, with 1,380 sq ft of living space on .138-acre lot (6,000 sq ft). The interior features spacious living room that opens up to the dining room, a family room, a walk-in closet, and detached 2 car garage. This home is located in a desirable neighborhood with nearby bus lines, shopping, restaurants, hiking and biking trails. Home is sold as is. Investor/Development Opportunity.
